-- Legrand First-Half Net Increases 79%; Raises 2010 Operating Margin Outlook
-- Vidya Root
-- 2010-07-29T05:30:07Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-07-29/legrand-first-half-net-increases-79-raises-2010-operating-margin-outlook.html

          
          
             Legrand SA said first-half net
income rose 79 percent to 192.6 million euros. Sales rose 5.4
percent to 1.91 billion euros. The company raised its full-year
target for adjusted operating margin to over 19 percent from
more than 18 percent previously.  
          
          


  


        